  "text": "The second paper on HNSCC exome sequencing, however, provided the information needed to develop a simple, useful measure of intra-tumor genetic heterogeneity. For the somatic mutations they identified, Stransky et al [CITATION_1] provided (in supplemental data) the number of DNA sequence reads that showed the reference DNA sequence and the number that showed the mutated sequence. We realized that this might be sufficient to let us assess the heterogeneity within each tumor.",
